new_window pixel 3

# Floating windows
## Notification area
for_window [class="Xfce4-notifyd"] floating enable; border none; focus mode_toggle
## Gnome do
for_window [class="Do"] floating enable; border none; focus mode_toggle

## Hamster time tracking app
for_window [class="Hamster-time-tracker"] floating enable; border 2px; focus mode_toggle
for_window [class="Time Tracker"] floating enable; border 2px; focus mode_toggle

## Music player
for_window [class="Clementine"] floating enable; border 2px; focus mode_toggle

## Thunderbird compose-window
for_window [instance="Msgcompose" class="Thunderbird"] floating enable; border 2px; focus mode_toggle

## xfce4-terminal
for_window [class="Xfce4-terminal"] floating enable; border 2px; focus mode_toggle

